org.tensorics.core.lang

Class DoubleTensorics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tensorics.core.lang.DoubleTensorics

  • public final class DoubleTensorics
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides delegate methods to a static instance of a TensoricSupport. This is for convenience purposes, so that a simple calculation does not have to inherit from the support class, but can statically import methods from this class.
